The paper discusses the use of machine learning tools for automatic music transcription, which falls under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SD) and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of evolutionary algorithms and self-adapting parameters also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
